//
// For example, it may be displayed like this:
//
// wandb: (41s) uploading artifact my-dataset (13/68 files)
// wandb:   (1.0s) my-dataset-14.h5 (1.2 MB / 100 MB)
// wandb:   (0.2s) my-dataset-15.h5 (43 MB / 100 MB)
